# CODEOWNERS - Defines who must review changes to critical files

# Default owners for everything
* @withterm/maintainers

# Security-critical files require admin approval
/.github/workflows/ @withterm/admins
/.github/CODEOWNERS @withterm/admins
/Cargo.toml @withterm/admins @withterm/maintainers
/Cargo.lock @withterm/maintainers

# Source code requires maintainer review
/src/ @withterm/maintainers
/tests/ @withterm/maintainers
/benches/ @withterm/maintainers

# Documentation can be reviewed by any maintainer
/docs/ @withterm/maintainers
*.md @withterm/maintainers
/README.md @withterm/maintainers
